title: Protect the suburbs from 'dominant' Northern Powerhouse cities, warns Tory MP
text: Politics Protect the suburbs from 'dominant' Northern Powerhouse cities, warns Tory MP Graham Brady, the chair of the powerful 1922 committee, has called on George Osborne to protect suburbs and rural areas in his devolution plans Senior Conservative MP Graham Brady has called for safeguards to George Osborne's devolution plans Photo: PA By Kate McCann , Senior Political Correspondent 12:01AM BST 14 Oct 2015
